57446   DEBUG:           event: {'speaker': 'Weissman', 'text': "No, my lord.{w}{br}We've searched the village, but the prince is nowhere to be found.{w}", 'text_position': None, 'width': None, 'style_nid': 'noir'}, set()
57446   DEBUG:           event: Event State: dialog
59778   DEBUG:           event: Event State: processing
59778   DEBUG:           event: Run Event Command: speak;Raydrik;You fool! We don't have much time.{w} I know that the prince is here.{w}{br}Round up the villagers and make them talk!{w}{br}We need to find him!{w};;;noir
59778   DEBUG:           event: Run Event Command: speak;Weissman;Yes, we are already doing that, my lord.{w}{br}But the villagers say that he's not here.{w}{br}He apparently left with the Fiana Freeblades,{w} to go save some village from a pirate attack.{w};;;noir
59778   DEBUG:           event: Run Event Command: speak;Raydrik;Fiana Freeblades?{br}What's that?{w};;;noir
59778   DEBUG:           event: Run Event Command: speak;Weissman;This village was originally the headquarters of a large group of brigands.{w}{br}A little over a decade ago, a travelling mercenary named Eyvel{w} cleared out the bandits and took over the village.{w}{br}She then stablished a militia to protect the nearby villages from bandit attacks.{w}{br}Apparently she's quite skilled with her sword...{w};;;noir
59778   DEBUG:           event: Run Event Command: speak;Raydrik;Hmm.... She could be a problem.{w};;;noir
